{"tid":21444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（左膠惡夢）奧地利今選總統！極右領袖有望上台！","createTime":"2016-12-03T23:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T03:45:33.000Z","uid":29314,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dbf21cd056c4fc9a8b0938dd2aa3a072a9bb8bea","tid":21444,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T23:17:22.000Z","msg":"奧地利今日的總統選舉，亦有可能由極右的奧地利自由黨（FPOe）候選人霍弗（Norbert Hofer，圖）&hellip;&hellip;成為二戰後西歐首個持極右立場的國家元首。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;45歲的霍弗在去年難民潮湧到歐洲的背景下，打着反移民旗號上位，痛批政府收留9萬名新移民，博得選民共鳴，&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n霍弗堅決仇外，曾揚言伊斯蘭教「把全世界當成戰場」。儘管近月難民人數大減，但霍弗憑打恐襲牌、描繪排斥「奧地利價值觀」的伊斯蘭社會，順利令選民繼續恐外。"},{"pid":"35581ff144ac221c242879c978abe578e30b3cbb","tid":21444,"uid":18604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T00:55:15.000Z","msg":"歷史重演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0c454fa76ed902113b906d18e835ea9c3e6ab7","tid":21444,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T00:57:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歷史重演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前有套戲講<br />\n<br />\n希特拉黎到現代，一樣可以上位做元首。"},{"pid":"12a588287e2aab86ef15f80aab7ce441b8d328aa","tid":21444,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T01:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>歷史重演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前有套戲講<br />\n<br />\n希特拉黎到現代，一樣可以上位做元首。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩戲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4104fdf1515fc710bdd4d3c122e32898a8af532","tid":21444,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T01:12:58.000Z","msg":"WWIII不是夢<br />\n大洗牌<br />\n機會_ _ ！_ _ ！"},{"pid":"dfa6e5973d0cfac3a7493c8700f94636c4c9f4ff","tid":21444,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T01:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>歷史重演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前有套戲講<br />\n<br />\n希特拉黎到現代，一樣可以上位做元首。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩戲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希特拉回來了"},{"pid":"1b8dea76edee892a08b11a6e90cb6fd2a489dc8a","tid":21444,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T01:33:00.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭教佢無講錯喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077326fbbaa995720190e0e3aa46582320777a59","tid":21444,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;歷史重演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前有套戲講<br />\n<br />\n希特拉黎到現代，一樣可以上位做元首。&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n咩戲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中文叫「希特拉回來了」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在德國電影&nbsp;Look Who&rsquo;s Back&nbsp;（「希特拉回來了」）一段即興場景中，演員&nbsp;Oliver Masucci 打扮成希特拉上街，竟受到德國民眾熱烈歡迎，更有人上前親吻、擁抱「希特拉」，祈求他「把勞改營帶回德國吧」。有不滿現狀的年輕人對「希特拉」盡訴衷腸：「我們要有人掌控大局，要有人說：『就這樣，不必討論了。』」"},{"pid":"b4cf252070472057035e5e8d6159f9c144855fc7","tid":21444,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:34:05.000Z","msg":"本來就應該要用concentration camp"},{"pid":"8036375efbe9675b5e214bbba7bd3113fdb76a79","tid":21444,"uid":27151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T09:02:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>歷史重演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前有套戲講<br />\n<br />\n希特拉黎到現代，一樣可以上位做元首。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩戲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希特拉回來了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希特拉支持左膠綠黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728ec984778da4ef73798f2f9a56fc67c10623c9","tid":21444,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:07:50.000Z","msg":"又燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8cdcab6f4a1b4a1137007fdba44e46018023c15","tid":21444,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:09:22.000Z","msg":"左極必右啦, 之前成個歐洲咁左膠, 係時候變成極右, 納粹一定改頭換面再出現"},{"pid":"ceb802b25abd245b4719fb42898d8c48412a9879","tid":21444,"uid":31452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:24:48.000Z","msg":"鬼叫左膠膠足咁多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884abdc155240ed7767e28b56b0298f099b1823e","tid":21444,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:45:33.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】奧地利總統選舉重選，票站調查顯示，前綠黨領袖范德貝倫以超過五成三的得票率勝出，他的極右自由黨對手霍費爾承認落敗。歐盟歡迎選舉結果，認為有助加強歐洲團結。<br />\n<br />\n兩粒鐘前已經有新聞話佢承認落敗 成班重打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}